                                    Contents
                                    --------
  ./docs/
    contains instructions for building, configuring, and running nginx-zmail

  ./extras/
    contains a sample nginx configuration file suitable for use with zmail

  ./sources/
    contains the pristine nginx source releases from http://nginx.net/

  ./nginx-<nnn>-zmail/
    contains the source tree which will be used to build nginx for zmail

  ./maintenance/
    should contain one patch for each version <nnn> of nginx, which describes
    the changes made by zmail to pristine nginx version <nnn>.
    these patches can be used in the future to port zmail versions to future
    versions of nginx

